"documents, locations and many other types."
msgstr ""

#: 67dad00c90054fbe8ff3ae13a47e1960 grammers.custom.Message.media_unread:1 of
msgid "Whether you have read the media in this message or not."
msgstr ""

#: 63001798ce3941a49d5d1bbc66e09896 grammers.custom.Message.media_unread:3 of
msgid "Most commonly, these are voice notes that you have not played yet."
msgstr ""

#: c75c5872a8d44a99b7eb5d81989db6c9 grammers.custom.Message.mentioned:1 of
