"message text)."
msgstr ""

#: 015062b1950d49038a1942eaf3819c86 grammers.custom.Message.message:1 of
msgid "The message's text."
msgstr ""

#: 27e70279e7d74f15b2eb685e7e9bb120 grammers.custom.Message.message:3 of
msgid "For service or empty messages, this will be None."
msgstr ""

#: ad607764f49a42449a8376d9b3030e43 grammers.custom.Message.message:5 of
msgid ""
"If the message has media, this text is the caption commonly displayed "
"underneath it."
msgstr ""

#: 8c3ba33e4c4f43fe8579bed33f148925 grammers.custom.Message.noforwards:1 of
msgid ""
"Whether this message is protected and thus cannot be forwarded; clients "
"should also prevent users from saving attached media (i.e. videos should "
"only be streamed, photos should be kept in RAM, et cetera)."
msgstr ""

#: f279b9d6402d4e9690f07ce4dff0e2a5 grammers.custom.Message.offline:1 of
msgid ""
"If set, the message was sent because of a scheduled action by the message"
