msgstr ""

#: 3260c6912ba64363a9d2326a5eca2faa grammers.custom.Message.out:1 of
msgid ""
"Whether the message is outgoing (i.e. you sent this message to some other"
" peer) or incoming (i.e. someone else sent it to you or the peer)."
msgstr ""

#: b7ca3db7ac5845bf8d728e2eec105ce9
#: grammers.custom.Message.paid_suggested_post_stars:1 of
